				%p
					A staple of the NASA brand is the “vertical type” treatment. To keep the app design feeling like NASA, even with the 
					%a{:href=>"https://developer.apple.com/library/ios/documentation/UserExperience/Conceptual/MobileHIG/Branding.html", :target=>"_blank"}
						absence of logos and heavy branding
					, we added vertical type to the category cells. We choose to display the “moment count” here, as we have relative control over the length of the label. This is the first screen users will see, so  it was a great opportunity to project the essence of NASA right out of the gate. 
